text:
@faz3 warm thoughts of thee though the day drizzles;
earnestly hoping for thy wellness;
close to my 💜 thou art as always;
thy face in my eyes;
my dearest Prince; 🚴🐎🐪🦒🕊️🐠🐥☕️📷💙

@faz3 after a day in the new year;
this torch of 💜 be ever burning;
seeing thy face elevates the weariness;
the malaise be eased;
it be a celebration of the moon and stars;
for one adores thee
completely as one 
waits for prayers 
to be answered; 🚴🐎🐪🦒🕊️🐠🐥🌳☕️📷💙
